                    <h3>3. City to Wilderness: Rapid Landscape Switching</h3>
                    <p>Because of the numerous mountains, Taiwan offers a "rapid landscape switch" rarely seen elsewhere. You can shop in modern Taipei and, within 3 to 4 hours, drive up to a high-altitude area of 3,000 meters.</p>
                    <p><strong>Popular Choices:</strong> Apart from the symbolic <strong>Jade Mountain (Yushan)</strong>, <strong>Hehuanshan</strong> is the most accessible high mountain. <strong>Xueshan (Snow Mountain)</strong> offers a chance to see rare subtropical snow scenes during January to March.</p>
